lyrics:
[Verse]
In the kitchen, flames ignite, my heart's desire
Measuring, sifting, stirring with burning fire
Whisking up a concoction, mixing molten dreams
A culinary symphony, where chaos seamlessly teems

[Chorus]
Baking the chaos, the sweetness takes hold
Rising with fury, this creation unfolds
Flames licking the edges, as I stand proud and tall
A metal masterpiece, a cake to conquer all
